Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.04,0:00:01.50,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.47,0:00:03.77,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,步入梦境的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.36,0:00:07.37,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,林间的阳光是如此灿烂…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.42,0:00:10.29,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,白雪的触感是如此寒冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.20,0:00:11.84,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.66,0:00:14.42,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,那个孩子却在哭泣…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.81,0:00:18.93,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,我至今也无法回忆起他哭泣着的面容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.69,0:01:57.36,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,亚由亚由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:04.05,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,抱歉　我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.47,0:02:06.16,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,今天有些太忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.76,0:02:09.13,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,我不是亚由亚由…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.76,0:02:11.17,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:12.70,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,月宫亚由…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.92,0:02:14.72,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,原来是很普通的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.56,0:02:18.92,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,我叫相泽祐一　请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.48,0:02:19.87,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:22.26,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,那么　我们走吧　亚由亚由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.86,0:02:23.81,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,呜咕～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.00,0:02:25.26,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,好奇怪的回答啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.47,0:02:26.32,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.46,0:02:37.88,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,今天的更好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:39.10,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:42.40,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,天下怎么会有哭着吃还会好吃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:43.36,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.21,0:02:49.12,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,祐一君…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:50.66,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:53.80,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,怎么？　要进行爱的表白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.82,0:02:55.28,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,才不会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.63,0:03:00.32,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.53,0:03:07.41,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,谢谢你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.03,0:03:14.22,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,呐　祐一君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:16.21,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,你喜欢妈妈吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:17.49,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,当然喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:18.32,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,为什么问这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.77,0:03:19.95,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,我也很喜欢妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:21.50,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,那又怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:23.46,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,就是这些…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.86,0:03:28.57,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.72,0:03:31.33,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:38.73,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,妈妈留下我走掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:44.62,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,就是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:02.18,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,我们明天也一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:02.99,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.89,0:04:04.40,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.98,0:04:06.90,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,嗯　只要亚由不介意就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:18.21,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,我与祐一君在一起…　就能够回忆起那些开心的事情了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.69,0:04:49.70,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,那个白痴！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:54.83,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,因果报应
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:04.50,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,啊呜～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:06.26,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,吓…　吓死我了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.52,0:05:08.94,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,这次又怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:10.84,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,是烟花啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.98,0:05:12.52,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,你从哪里买来这种东西的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.93,0:05:15.12,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,真琴　你想玩烟花了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:15.47,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:17.52,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,啊…　嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.24,0:05:20.26,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,这样的事情对我说一声就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.74,0:05:24.26,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,如果真琴想做什么的话　我也会帮你想办法的
